data.description: Introducing a charming single-family residence located in the diverse and prominent neighborhood of Maxwell Park. This 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers 1,082 square feet of living space and a lot size of 3,484 square feet. Built in 1925, it boasts a blend of classic and modern features, including new interior and exterior paint, fresh landscaping in the front and back yards, an updated fireplace, and stylish tile flooring throughout. One of the highlights of this humble abode is the new Central Heating and Cooling System, ensuring comfort year-round. Additionally, it features a convenient walk-in tub for relaxation and ease of use.   Step inside and discover a beautifully designed floor plan with a cozy kitchen and a lovely dining area, perfect for gatherings. From the back deck, you can enjoy stunning views overlooking the Bay Area. This property is in close proximity to shopping centers, numerous restaurants, and easy access to the 580 freeway for commuting. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this remarkable property your new home.  --
